reviewText: I love this movie so much. I remember watching it around the time it was released which was years ago and had been super excited to watch it again. I finally ordered it off Amazon so my fianc and I could watch it together. He had never seen it before so I was thrilled to show him. He loved it as well! I highly recommend this film if you're into horror.
